Warning: Read all instructions for your wax melt and warmer prior to use. To prevent fire of injury: Remove melt from packaging. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Use within sight. Do not touch hot wax. Hot wax can cause burn injury. Allow wax to harden before touching or handling. To avoid splatter, smoke or flame, do not add water or fragrance oil to wax. Keep melts clear of debris. Do not attempt to use melt as a candle. Why do some wax melts seem to last longer than others? The temperature of the tart warmer is the single biggest factor to influence how long a wax melt will produce an effective scent throw. Some tart warmers get hotter than others. Tart warmers that get really hot will produce a higher intensity fragrance, but the fragrance will dissipate much sooner. Tart warmers that dont get as hot tend to produce a less intense, but longer lasting aroma. Therefore, it is a tradeoff of intensity versus endurance.

Warning: Read all instructions for your wax melt and warmer prior to use. To prevent fire of injury: Remove melt from packaging. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Use within sight. Do not touch hot wax. Hot wax can cause burn injury. Allow wax to harden before touching or handling. To avoid splatter, smoke or flame, do not add water or fragrance oil to wax. Keep melts clear of debris. Do not attempt to use melt as a candle. Why do some wax melts seem to last longer than others? The temperature of the tart warmer is the single biggest factor to influence how long a wax melt will produce an effective scent throw. Some tart warmers get hotter than others. Tart warmers that get really hot will produce a higher intensity fragrance, but the fragrance will dissipate much sooner. Tart warmers that dont get as hot tend to produce a less intense, but longer lasting aroma. Therefore, it is a tradeoff of intensity versus endurance.

6in LED Timer Pillar Dipped Faith Hope Love

Our new​ led​ pillars are even better than ever! All of our​ battery operated​ pillar​ candles​ now have a 3 in 1 feature that allows you to choose how you would like to use your candle. They have the option to turn the candle switch on, off or use the auto timer feature (6 hours on, 18 hours off). Perfect for when you need to have your candle on longer or for when you need to turn your candle off sooner.

Your customers will love the versatile functionality of th​ese! ​​ Each pillar is Hand dipped​ in PA, so these will be a super addition to your handmade in the USA section of your store. Available in 3x6" and 3x4" sizes and requires 3 AAA batteries (not included). Pick from several styles: grungy dipped, plain, melted drip or smooth.  Due to the handmade nature of this product, there can be some slight color variations in the wax.

Our new​ led​ pillars are even better than ever! All of our​ battery operated​ pillar​ candles​ now have a 3 in 1 feature that allows you to choose how you would like to use your candle. They have the option to turn the candle switch on, off or use the auto timer feature (6 hours on, 18 hours off). Perfect for when you need to have your candle on longer or for when you need to turn your candle off sooner. Your customers will love the versatile functionality of th​ese! ​​ Each pillar is Hand dipped​ in PA, so these will be a super addition to your handmade in the USA section of your store. Available in 3x6" and 3x4" sizes and requires 3 AAA batteries (not included). Pick from several styles: grungy dipped, plain, melted drip or smooth. Due to the handmade nature of this product, there can be some slight color variations in the wax.

column1: 6 pcs 4in LED Dipped Timer Tapers, Black
column4:
6 pcs 4in LED Dipped Timer Tapers, Black. Package of 6 LED battery operated timer taper candles.

These tapers are wax dipped and have a timer. The timer function will start on its own once the batteries are inserted. Timer is on 6 hours and off for 18 hours. LED candle bulb tip is also dipped in wax. Tapers measure approximately 4.5 inches long and are about 3/4" in diameter and the base is tapered to fit any standard taper holder. We offer eight color options - burgundy, black, brown, cream, rust, red, farmhouse gray or white. These are also known as flicker taper candles or dipped flicker candlesticks. When lit these candles will create a beautiful warm glow and are a great addition for any style home decor. LED candles create the look of a burning candle without the dangers of real fire which makes it much safer for families with pets or young children. Each 4" taper candle uses 1 "AA" battery, not included.

Available in packs of 6 ONLY. This listing is for 1 pack of 6 tapers.

column1: 6 pcs 7in LED Dipped Timer Tapers, Black
column4:
6 pcs 7in LED Dipped Timer Tapers, Black. Package of 6 LED battery operated timer taper candles.

These tapers are wax dipped and have a timer. The timer function will start on its own once the batteries are inserted. Timer is on 6 hours and off for 18 hours. LED candle bulb tip is also dipped in wax. Tapers measure approximately 7 inches long and are about 3/4" in diameter and the base is tapered to fit any standard taper holder. We offer eight color options - burgundy, black, brown, cream, rust, red, farmhouse gray or white. These are also known as flicker taper candles or dipped flicker candlesticks. When lit these candles will create a beautiful warm glow and are a great addition for any style home decor. LED candles create the look of a burning candle without the dangers of real fire which makes it much safer for families with pets or young children. Each 7" taper candle uses 2 "AA" batteries, not included.

Available in packs of 6 ONLY. This listing is for 1 pack of 6 tapers.

Handcrafted and painted small wooden bee cut-out with mesh wings.  Amish made in Lancaster County, PA.  Great addition to any crafting project or you could add a hanger for a cute touch to your spring/summer wall decor.  Wooden bee measures approximately 6-1/2" long x 6-1/2" wide including wing span (wooden bee body is approx. 2-3/4" wide) x 1/2" thick.

Handcrafted and hand painted wooden garden gnome.  Amish made in Lancaster County, PA.  No two gnomes are alike!  Slight imperfections in the wood and painting due to the handmade nature.  These are not finely painted and are front finished only.  Great porch sitter or garden decor.  Wooden garden gnome measures approximately 19.5" Tall x 12" wide including hat span (garden gnome body is approx. 6" wide) x 1" thick.  Will not except special orders/requests for particular colors or designs, these are randomly selected for each customer.  Only ONE gnome piece per price not four gnomes as shown in picture.

column1: 6 pcs 7in LED Dipped Timer Tapers, Brown
column4:
6 pcs 7in LED Dipped Timer Tapers, Brown. Package of 6 LED battery operated timer taper candles.

These tapers are wax dipped and have a timer. The timer function will start on its own once the batteries are inserted. Timer is on 6 hours and off for 18 hours. LED candle bulb tip is also dipped in wax. Tapers measure approximately 7 inches long and are about 3/4" in diameter and the base is tapered to fit any standard taper holder. We offer eight color options - burgundy, black, brown, cream, rust, red, farmhouse gray or white. These are also known as flicker taper candles or dipped flicker candlesticks. When lit these candles will create a beautiful warm glow and are a great addition for any style home decor. LED candles create the look of a burning candle without the dangers of real fire which makes it much safer for families with pets or young children. Each 7" taper candle uses 2 "AA" batteries, not included.

Available in packs of 6 ONLY. This listing is for 1 pack of 6 tapers.
